//Protection from Evil
@70023 = ~Wand of Protection from Evil~
@70024 = ~When activated, the wand creates a magical barrier around the recipient at a distance of one foot. The barrier has three effects: First, it bestows a +2 bonus to the recipient's Armor Class and Saving Throws against attacks from evil-aligned opponents; second, it prevents summoned fiends from attacking the recipient; third, it makes the recipient immune to charm-based spells or effects (e.g. Charm Person, Charm Person or Mammal, Domination, and so on).

STATISTICS:
(Abjuration)

Charge abilities:
– Protection from Evil
  – +2 AC bonus against attacks from Evil creatures
