//Chill Touch
@70031 = ~Wand of Chill Touch~
@70032 = ~When activated, a blue glow encompasses the wielder's hand, and <PRO_HESHE> uses this energy to attack the life force of of any creature upon which the wielder makes a successful melee attack. The touched creature must make a Save vs. Wand or suffer 1d4 points of cold damage and receive a -1 THAC0 penalty for 1 turn after being struck.

An undead creature suffers no damage or to-hit penalty from Chill Touch, but will be affected by panic for 2 turns unless it successfully makes a Save vs. Spell.

STATISTICS:
(Necromancy)

Charge abilities:
– Chill Touch
  – Living:
    – Cold energy attack
    – -1 penalty to THAC0 to target for 1 turn
  – Undead:
    – Suffer panic for 2 turns
  Damage:
    – 1d4 cold damage
  Range: Touch
  Duration: 1 turn
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


